{"arkId":"cl010100750","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010100750","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre octogonale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre octogonale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1625 - 1650","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1625,"endYear":1650,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Champagnieu, Claude","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1658","place":"Lyon","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10060","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre octogonale ; bo\u00eetier en cristal de roche taill\u00e9 \u00e0 facettes et biseaut\u00e9, muni d\u0027armatures grav\u00e9es de feuillages et de stries. Pendant en forme de chapiteau. Cadran grav\u00e9 pr\u00e9sentant un d\u00e9cor sym\u00e9trique : au milieu de rinceaux fleuris apparaissent deux chiens courant, deux femmes nues soutenant une corbeille de fruits, un mascaron coiff\u00e9 de pampres. Au centre du cercle horaire \u00e0 chiffres romains, une vue de village anim\u00e9 d\u0027un vagabond protant un baluchon et tenant un b\u00e2ton. Echappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet ajour\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux fleuris. Piliers en forme de balustre.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : C Champagnieu\/A Lyon [signature ponctu\u00e9e d\u0027une fleurette)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,2","displayDimension":"5,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,1","displayDimension":"3,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,3","displayDimension":"2,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Lyon (Rh\u00f4ne-Alpes = Rh\u00f4ne Alpes-\u003ERh\u00f4ne)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Claudius C\u00f4te (1881-1956), \u00e0 Lyon ; legs Mme Marie-Fran\u00e7oise C\u00f4te, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 9 juillet 1961","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme C\u00f4te, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. C\u00f4te, Claudius","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"02\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"16\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"09\/07\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisit